\title{Og}

\taxon{skill}

\meta{description}{'## Overview'}

\subtree{
\title{og - Observational Bridge Time Travel Skill}
\subtree{
\title{Overview}
\p{The \code{\startverb og\stopverb} skill maintains plurigrid fork synchronization while cherry-picking from the original (og) remote. It implements time-travel exercises through an observational bridge pattern for DuckDB buffers tracking ersatz Emacs interactions.}
}

\subtree{
\title{Core Concepts}
\subtree{
\title{Observational Bridge Type}
\pre{\startverb
OG Remote ────[cherry-pick]────→ Plurigrid Fork
     ↑                                  │
     │                                  │
  [time-travel]              [DuckDB buffer]
     │                                  │
     └──── CRDT.el sexp state ←────────┘
\stopverb}
}

\subtree{
\title{3-MATCH Chromatic Identity for Git Operations}
\ul{
\li{\strong{SEED-WORLD}: Git commit SHA}
\li{\strong{COLOR-WORLD}: Gay.jl color from commit timestamp}
\li{\strong{FINGERPRINT-WORLD}: DuckDB buffer hash}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{Tracked Interactions}
\ol{
\li{\strong{crdt.el sexp state} - Intermediate collaborative editing state}
\li{\strong{Gay.jl invocations} - Color generation calls with seed/index}
\li{\strong{GayMCP rewriting} - Self-modifying protocol operations}
}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{Usage}
\subtree{
\title{Cherry-Pick with Time Travel}
\pre{\startverb
# Fetch from og remote with color tracking
og fetch --track-colors

# Cherry-pick specific commit with DuckDB buffer
og cherry-pick <sha> --buffer-to-duckdb

# Time travel to previous state
og time-travel --to-round <drand_round>
\stopverb}
}

\subtree{
\title{DuckDB Buffer Operations}
\pre{\startverb
-- Query crdt.el interaction history
SELECT * FROM crdt_sexp_buffer
WHERE session_id = current_session()
ORDER BY timestamp DESC;

-- Gay.jl color tracking
SELECT seed, index, hex_color, girard_polarity
FROM gay_color_invocations
WHERE timestamp > now() - interval '1 hour';
\stopverb}
}

\subtree{
\title{Self-Rewriting Protocol}
\p{The skill tracks when GayMCP rewrites itself by monitoring:}

\ul{
\li{Seed state changes}
\li{Color palette mutations}
\li{3-MATCH triangle verification failures}
}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{Configuration}
\pre{\startverb
{
  "og": {
    "remote": "og",
    "branch": "asi-skillz",
    "duckdb_path": "~/.og/time_travel.duckdb",
    "track_gay_jl": true,
    "track_crdt_el": true,
    "drand_beacon": "quicknet"
  }
}
\stopverb}
}

\subtree{
\title{Integration with music-topos}
\p{The skill connects to the Blume-Capel ergodic random walk:}

\ul{
\li{+1 cherry-pick: Accept commit (ferromagnetic)}
\li{-1 cherry-pick: Reject commit (antiferromagnetic)}
\li{0 cherry-pick: BEAVER - defer decision (vacancy)}
}

\p{Möbius inversion tracks the cumulative cherry-pick decisions.}
}
}